Language: uz

00:00:00.730 --> 00:00:02.180
Toping-chi, soat necha bo‘ldi?

00:00:02.180 --> 00:00:03.670
&gt;&gt; Ovqatlanish vaqti keldimi?

00:00:03.670 --> 00:00:04.340
&gt;&gt; Yo‘q.

00:00:04.340 --> 00:00:07.390
Talabalar o‘zlarining metodlarini 
aniqlash va chaqirish vaqti keldi.

00:00:07.390 --> 00:00:10.860
&gt;&gt; To‘xtang, ular mutlaqo yangi 
usulni aniqlab chaqirishlari kerakmi?

00:00:10.860 --> 00:00:11.970
U nima deb nomlangan?

00:00:11.970 --> 00:00:13.702
&gt;&gt; U createOrderSummary deb nomlanadi.

00:00:13.702 --> 00:00:17.100
U ilovaga kiritilgan ma’lumotlarni 
umumlashtirishi va uni matn shaklida 

00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.490
ko‘rsatishi kerak.

00:00:18.490 --> 00:00:20.070
&gt;&gt; Sizningcha, ular tayyormi?

00:00:20.070 --> 00:00:21.170
&gt;&gt; Menimcha ha.

00:00:21.170 --> 00:00:25.142
Menimcha, bizning polaponlarimiz qanotlarini yoyib, 
uchib ketish vaqti keldi.

00:00:25.142 --> 00:00:30.712
[Qushlarning ovozi]

00:00:30.712 --> 00:00:33.472
Endi biz ilovani mana bunday 
ko‘rinishga o‘zgartiramiz.

00:00:33.472 --> 00:00:35.956
Agar siz miqdorni o‘zgartirsangiz va 
"Order" tugmasini bossangiz, ekrandagi 

00:00:35.956 --> 00:00:38.180
buyurtmalar ro‘yxati uzunroq bo‘ladi.

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:42.270
Bu MainActivity yuqori darajadasida 
mana bunday bo‘ladi.

00:00:42.270 --> 00:00:44.950
Ilovadagi "Order" tugmachasini bosganimizda, 
ushbu metodni chaqiramiz, 

00:00:44.950 --> 00:00:48.850
so‘ng uning ichida calculatePrice 
metodini chaqiramiz.

00:00:48.850 --> 00:00:51.920
Metod input parametrlarisiz 
chaqiriladi, u barcha 

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:56.090
ko‘rsatmalarni bajarib, 
umimiy narxni qaytaradi.

00:00:56.090 --> 00:00:58.590
submitOrder metodi narxga ega 
bo‘lgach, biz createOrderSummary 

00:00:58.590 --> 00:01:02.450
summani shu narx bilan chaqira olamiz.

00:01:02.450 --> 00:01:04.650
Shunday qilib, biz ushbu metodga narx 
qo‘yamiz va keyin uning 

00:01:04.650 --> 00:01:06.970
ichidagi ko‘rsatmalarni bajaramiz.

00:01:06.970 --> 00:01:10.100
Metod yakuniy matnni qaytaradi.

00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:13.300
Keyin ushbu kod satrlari matnni ko‘rsatadi.

00:01:14.710 --> 00:01:16.050
Bu kodni bajarish uchun 

00:01:16.050 --> 00:01:17.650
orderSummary metodini yaratamiz.

00:01:18.690 --> 00:01:21.110
Ekranda ilova shunday 
ko‘rinishda bo‘lishi kerak.

00:01:21.110 --> 00:01:22.890
Ilgari ko‘rsatilgandek.

00:01:24.290 --> 00:01:27.950
Avvalo, MainActivity da
yangi metod yaratishimiz kerak.

00:01:27.950 --> 00:01:30.150
Metodni createOrderSummary deb nomlaymiz.

00:01:30.150 --> 00:01:32.550
Input parametri son qiymatli 

00:01:32.550 --> 00:01:34.450
buyurtma narxi bo‘ladi.

00:01:34.450 --> 00:01:36.780
Oxirida metod ushbu xabarni qaytaradi.

00:01:36.780 --> 00:01:39.470
O‘zingiz boshqa biror nom tanglashingiz 
va undan foydalanishingiz mumkin.

00:01:39.470 --> 00:01:41.290
Foydalanuvchi tanlab kiritgan 

00:01:41.290 --> 00:01:46.030
miqdorni hosil bo‘lgan qiymat 
bilan taqqoslab, tekshirig.

00:01:46.030 --> 00:01:46.940
Oxirida Thank you! -ni qo‘shing.

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:52.527
Ikkinchi bosqichda, yangi 
submitOrder metodni chaqiramiz.

00:01:53.780 --> 00:01:57.480
Ushbu satrni submitOrder 
metodiga qo‘shganingizda, 

00:01:57.480 --> 00:02:00.220
metodning natijasini ekranda aks ettiring.

00:02:00.220 --> 00:02:01.500
Tugatganingizda ushbu 
katakchalarni belgilang.

